data.description: **Meticulously Maintained 3-Bedroom Home with Impressive Upgrades and Prime Location**    Welcome to this home nestled in a quiet cul-de-sac and just minutes away from Fort Carson and Peterson Air Force Base. With its thoughtfully designed interior, attractive features, and outdoor spaces, this home offers the perfect blend of comfort and convenience.**    You’ll be greeted by the inviting atmosphere of a neutral color palette that complements the interior's modern design. The main floor boasts a spacious front office complete with French doors that will be a versatile space for your home office or flex needs.**    The heart of the home is the well-appointed kitchen, featuring sleek espresso cabinets that beautifully contrast with the stunning granite countertops. Stainless steel appliances add a touch of sophistication, while the practical coffee bar/cabinet drop zone in the mudroom ensures functionality and organization.**    You’ll have plenty of space to entertain with a covered patio extending to the fully fenced and xeriscaped backyard. Perfect for gatherings, barbecues, and relaxation and it keeps utility bills in check.**    Upstairs, discover the tranquil haven of the primary bedroom suite. The adjoining 5-piece bathroom is a relaxing retreat, boasting a deep soaking tub, an oversized shower, double vanity with granite countertops, and increased-height cabinets.    Two additional well-proportioned bedrooms and the laundry room complete the second floor. The unfinished basement is stubbed for a future bathroom and provides ample storage space or potential for a home gym.    The home's strategic location offers an easy commute for military personnel just minutes from Fort Carson and Peterson Air Force Base.    Don't miss the opportunity to make this meticulously maintained home yours. Schedule a showing today and experience the perfect blend of modern living, thoughtful design, and convenience in one package.
